<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.6">
<l>kiṟiyeṉa niṉaimiṉ kīḻmai ceyyātē</l>
<l>yuṟiyamar veṇṇe yuṇṭavaṉ kōyiṉ</l>
<l>maṟiyoṭu piṇaicēr māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>neṟipaṭa vatuvē niṉaivatu nalamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Think [that is] the way without committing lowly acts.</l>
<l>Goodness is thinking of that correctly</l>
<l>– Māliruñcōlai joined by does with fawns,</l>
<l>the temple of him who ate the butter that was in the pot net.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
